<topic class="Popup" template="Default" status="Under Construction" modified="2022-03-11T10:16:41.004Z" lasteditedby="Adam" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">MotionDesigner-Period-Ratio</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Motion Design Considerations:<keyword translate="true">Dynamic Performance</keyword><keyword translate="true">Natural Frequency</keyword><keyword translate="true">Period Ratio of the Cam Follower</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><table styleclass="MotionPupup" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">Here, the term </text><text styleclass="Interface" translate="true">&apos;period&apos; </text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">is a</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> time period.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Interface" translate="true">Period Ratio: </text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">a </text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold; color:#ff0000;" translate="true">number</text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true"> that is the ratio of two time periods:</text></para>
          <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">the period of the motion.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">the period of the fundamental vibration of the mechanical system that is driven by the motion.</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">Thus, it is possible to have a Low Period-Ratio even with slow-speed machines, when the period of vibration is high, with a low frequency,</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Interface" translate="true">High-values, </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">typically &gt; 10, indicates a</text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true"> stiff, small inertia/mass.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Interface" translate="true">Low values,</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> typically &lt; 5, indicate a</text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true"> compliant, large inertia/mass.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Interface" translate="true">Period-Ratio</text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true"> is a characteristic of the machine that varies with the speed.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">Aim to keep the </text><text styleclass="Interface" translate="true">Period Ratio &gt; 10</text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;" translate="true">.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
</topic>
